high_descs: turn left and walk to the end of the kitchen island counter on the right, then turn right and walk over to the kitchen stove at the end of the room, and turn left to walk to the coffee maker
grab the butter knife on the kitchen counter to the right of the coffee maker
turn left and walk over to the kitchen island on the left
cut up the potato on the kitchen island counter
turn around and walk to the sink ahead, then turn right and look upwards a bit
place the butter knife down on the kitchen counter to the left
turn right and walk over to the kitchen island counter
grab a potato slice off of the kitchen counter
turn around and walk to the kitchen stove on the right side of the room
place the potato slice in the microwave above the kitchen stove, cook it, then take it back out
turn around and walk over to the kitchen sink on the right side of the room
place the potato slice inside of the sink on the left
anns.task_desc: place a microwaved potato slice inside of the sink

high_descs: Turn left, then right around the counter and face the counter on your left.
Pick up the silver knife from the counter in front of you.
Turn left and face the green island on your left.
Slice the potato in front of you on the island.
Turn left and face the stove in front of you.
Place the silver knife on the counter to your left.
Turn right and face the counter in front of you.
Take a potato slice from the counter in front of you.
Turn left and head towards the microwave on top of the stove.
Heat up the potato slice in the microwave and take it out.
Turn around and face the sink on your right.
Put the potato slice in the sink in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a hot potato slice in the sink.

high_descs: Walk to your left, turn right near the fridge, walk straight toward the stove and turn left to face the dishwasher.
Pick up the knife next to the coffee maker.
Walk to the left and turn to the left to face a table in the middle of the room.
Cut the potato nearest to the edge of the table.
Turn around and go back to the dishwasher.
Put the knife on the counter top on top of the dishwasher.
Turn around and go back to the table in the middle of the room again.
Pick up a slice of the potato.
Walk to the left and walk straight to the microwave oven.
Open the microwave, put the slice of potato inside, close the microwave, heat it for a few seconds, pick up the potato and close the microwave.
Turn around, walk straight and turn to the sink.
Put the slice of potato next to the fork in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked potato next to the fork in the sink.

high_descs: Walk around the left side of the table to the other side of the room and turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the knife laying on the counter.
Turn around and approach the kitchen table.
Cut the potato on the counter into slices.
Turn around and approach the sink.
Place the knife on the left side of the sink.
Turn around and walk forward to the kitchen table.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Turn to the left and walk forward to face the stove.
Heat the potato in the microwave above the stove and remove it.
Turn around, walk halfway across the room and turn to the right to face the sink.
Place the potato slice in the sink.
anns.task_desc: To cut a potato, heat a slice, as well as place it in the sink.

high_descs: Walk to the opposite corner of the table and turn left to face the counter with a coffee maker on it.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around and walk forward to face the table.
Cut the potato that is close to the edge of the table.
Turn around to face the counter to the left of the sink.
Place the knife on the counter.
Turn around and walk forward to face the table.
Pick up a slice of potato from on the table.
Turn to the right and walk forward to face the microwave.
Heat the potato slice in the microwave and remove it.
Turn around and walk forward and then face the sink on the right.
Place the potato slice in the sink.
anns.task_desc: To cut plus head a potato slice as well as set it in the sink.
